content:
DomainCollisionOptions Enum

Definition

Specifies additional information about a forest trust collision when the stem.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType* property value is ForestTrustCollisionType.

In this Article

[System.Flags]
public enum DomainCollisionOptions
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
System.Enum
DomainCollisionOptions

Fields

NetBiosNameDisabledByAdmin

The forest trust NetBIOS record was disabled by administrative action.
NetBiosNameDisabledByConflict

The forest trust NetBIOS record was disabled due to a conflict with an existing NetBIOS record.
None

No action has occurred.
SidDisabledByAdmin

The forest trust SID was disabled by administrative action.
SidDisabledByConflict

The forest trust SID was disabled due to a conflict with an existing SID.
